  <activity class="@textGrid.WordSearch" name="sopa" code="">
   <description />
   <messages>
    <cell type="initial">
     <style>
      <font family="Arial" size="26" bold="true" />
      <color foreground="0xFFFFFF" background="0x009900" />
     </style>
     <p>Encuentra 8 palabras escondidas.</p>
    </cell>
    <cell avoidOverlapping="true" image="i01-bienhecho.jpg" type="final">
     <style>
      <font family="Arial" size="28" bold="true" />
      <color foreground="0xFFFFFF" background="0x006666" />
     </style>
     <p>¡Muy bien!</p>
    </cell>
   </messages>
   <settings margin="8" report="true" reportActions="false">
    <helpWindow showSolution="true" />
    <container bgColor="0xCC00CC">
     <gradient source="0xFF9999" dest="0xFFFFFF" angle="0" />
     <image name="libertador-resized.jpg" tiled="true" />
     <counters time="true" actions="true" score="true" />
    </container>
    <window bgColor="0x00FFFF" border="true" />
   </settings>
   <textGrid rows="9" columns="10" cellWidth="50.0" cellHeight="40.0" border="true">
    <style margin="3">
     <font family="Arial" size="72" bold="true" />
     <color foreground="0xFFFF00" background="0xCC0000" />
    </style>
    <text>
     <row>PERÚCC***</row>
     <row>*L**HO***</row>
     <row>A*A*IRE**</row>
     <row>R**NLDJ**</row>
     <row>M***EIÉ**</row>
     <row>A****LR*S</row>
     <row>S****LC*E</row>
     <row>*****EI*D</row>
     <row>SANMARTÍN</row>
     <row>*****AO*A</row>
    </text>
   </textGrid>
   <clues>
    <clue id="0">PERÚ</clue>
    <clue id="1">CHILE</clue>
    <clue id="2">CORDILLERA</clue>
    <clue id="3">EJÉRCITO</clue>
    <clue id="4">ANDES</clue>
    <clue id="5">PLAN</clue>
    <clue id="6">SANMARTÍN</clue>
    <clue id="7">ARMAS</clue>
   </clues>
  </activity>
  <activity class="@associations.SimpleAssociation" name="unir_2" code="">
   <description />
   <messages>
    <cell type="initial">
     <style>
      <font family="Arial" size="30" bold="true" />
      <color background="0xFFCCCC" />
     </style>
     <p>Unir cada imagen con su nombre.</p>
    </cell>
    <cell avoidOverlapping="true" image="i01-i01-i01-bienhecho.jpg" type="final">
     <style>
      <font family="Arial" size="36" bold="true" />
      <color foreground="0xFFFFFF" background="0x006600" />
     </style>
     <p>¡Muy bien!</p>
    </cell>
   </messages>
   <settings margin="8" report="true" reportActions="false">
    <container bgColor="0xC0C0C0">
     <gradient source="0x990099" dest="0xFFFFFF" angle="0" />
     <counters time="true" actions="true" score="true" />
    </container>
    <window bgColor="0xC0C0C0" transparent="true" border="true" />
   </settings>
   <cells rows="4" cols="1" cellWidth="225.0" cellHeight="148.0" border="true" id="primary">
    <style>
     <color background="0xFFFFFF" inactive="0xFFFFFF" />
    </style>
    <shaper class="@Rectangular" cols="1" rows="4" />
    <cell image="1-resized.jpg">
     <style borderStroke="0.7" markerStroke="5.0">
      <color background="0x666600" />
     </style>
    </cell>
    <cell image="2-resized.jpg" />
    <cell image="3-resized.jpg" />
    <cell image="4-resized.jpg" />
   </cells>
   <cells rows="4" cols="1" cellWidth="316.0" cellHeight="99.0" border="true" id="secondary">
    <style borderStroke="0.7" markerStroke="5.0">
     <font family="Arial" size="20" bold="true" />
     <color background="0xFFCCFF" inactive="0xFFFFFF" />
     <gradient source="0xFF99FF" dest="0xFFFFFF" angle="0" />
    </style>
    <shaper class="@Rectangular" cols="1" rows="4" />
    <cell>
     <p>Los realistas españoles en Chile impedían la libertad, controlando tras los Andes.</p>
    </cell>
    <cell>
     <p>San Martín ideó un plan audaz para sorprender y vencer a los españoles.</p>
    </cell>
    <cell>
     <p>En El Plumerillo comenzó a preparar al ejército con víveres, armas y abrigo.</p>
    </cell>
    <cell>
     <p>El pueblo colaboró cosiendo ropa, cargando provisiones y apoyando con gran patriotismo.</p>
    </cell>
   </cells>
   <cells rows="4" cols="1" cellWidth="50.0" cellHeight="30.0" border="true" id="solvedPrimary">
    <style />
    <shaper class="@Rectangular" cols="1" rows="4" />
    <cell image="i01-i01-bienhecho.jpg" />
    <cell image="i01-i01-bienhecho.jpg" />
    <cell image="i01-i01-bienhecho.jpg" />
    <cell image="i01-i01-bienhecho.jpg" />
   </cells>
   <scramble times="31" primary="true" secondary="true" />
   <layout position="AB" />
  </activity>
